These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid
House: palace, wooden
1. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Flower           | orchid | daffodil |
| House   | wooden     | palace  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, coral
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, police-officer
1. the musician is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Color         | coral   | amber      |
| Job   | musician | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, plum
1. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Sport   | skateboarding | rugby    |
| Food     | nectarine | plum |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, montecristo
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, dahlia
1. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the right of the vegafina-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | montecristo |
| Flower   | aconite | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, july
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, golf
1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Birthday   | july | october |
| Sport     | golf    | cricket    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-6::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, motorbike
City: hamburg, venice
1. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |        2        |
| Transport   | motorbike  | subway     |
| City        | hamburg | venice |

